description:
Clear quartz gwindel 

Oberaar Glacier, Grimsel area, Hasli-Valley, Bern, Switzerland

Quartz crystals that grew along and are slightly rotated around a single a-axis. This results in twisted and tabular crystals. The twist reflects the handedness of the quartz crystals. With increasing distance from the base
- right-handed gwindels twist clockwise.
- left-handed gwindels twist counter-clockwise.

Source: https://www.mindat.org/min-39374.html
CA0

description:
💙Blue Tiger Eye 
闪电蓝虎眼💙

It is a highly soothing stone that can reduce your stress, ease your anxieties, and increase your calm and relaxation. 

It helps in easing eye problems as well as fortifying the blood. It effectively slows down an intense metabolism. 

It is actually known as the stone of good fortune and good luck.

1.蓝虎眼石对应喉轮，蓝色光对应太阳轮、黑色光对应海底轮，所以对人的消化系统有帮助，对暴饮暴食造成的身体不适有很好的重新净化的作用，从而消除不适的感觉。而且能够化病排毒，有清洗杂气的功效。

2.能激宣布勇气，带来决心，坚定信念，使人英勇。能软化顽固、顽固，使之合理化，而能跟的上年代潮流，不致被筛选，带来积极进取的人生观与干事精力。蓝虎眼还有化病排毒，清洁杂气成效。蓝虎眼石有一项很格外的功用，即是能够加快事物的构成。

3.灵性作用。辟邪保平安，招财纳福等都是虎眼石的灵性作用。

description:
💙蓝晶石｜Kyanite💙

Communication | 表达能力

Blue Kyanite opens the throat chakra, encouraging communication and self-expression.  It cuts through fears and blockages, helping to speak one’s truth.  It is very useful for public speakers and performers as it strengthens the voice and heals the throat and the larynx.
 蓝晶石对应喉轮，能协助清理喉轮的负面能量，对于时常语塞无法顺畅表达的人，蓝晶石能协助清除阻塞，帮助顺畅沟通。
 Emotional | 稳定情绪

Kyanite has a calming effect on the whole being, bringing tranquility.  It encourages psychic abilities and communication on all levels.  It drives away anger, frustration, confusion and stress and helps to provide a capacity for linear and logical thought.
 蓝晶石对应眉心轮，具有提高洞察力、直觉力、促进灵性觉知，并帮助恢复冷静思考，帮助安稳情绪。

Mindset | 突破转换

Blue Kyanite can be used to enhance communication and mental clarity.
 蓝晶石能协助转换新思维，协助重新调整自我。

💚 Phantom Quartz is a variety of quartz that has formed over pre-existing crystals over the course of a million years.  During its slow formation, such crystal has absorbed knowledge & wisdom that can help you to put the past into perspective & assist you in having a smooth transition so that you’ll know what’s your next step should be.

💚 The healing energies of this crystal will help you to overcome stagnation in your life/relationships & make a breakthrough in your personal/professional life.  Phantom Quartz will store, transmit & amplify your energies to give a fresh burst of inspiration that will help you live your life with zest & enthusiasm.

💚 Phantom Quartz is also known as a fantastic aura cleanser that helps remove negative energies in your auric field & put your chakras into alignment.  It promotes a positive flow of energies in your life by removing negative emotion & thoughts, stimulates concentration, memory & thinking process.

💚 In FengShui, Green Phantom Quartz is believed to bring about an abundance of wealth luck, career stability, authority & promotional luck.

💰 牡丹花的寓意是富贵吉祥、繁荣昌盛。

💰 牡丹又名洛阳花、富贵花，是中国特有的花卉之一，被誉为花中之王。牡丹雍容大度，花开富贵，是吉祥富贵的象征。牡丹花开之时繁花似锦、绚丽灿烂，其美丽花姿让人为之倾倒，雍容典雅、富贵祥和的形象寓意国家繁荣昌盛、兴旺发达；人们对于牡丹的喜爱，精神和优秀品格的象征，也成为美的化身，有纯洁与爱情的象征意义

💚 绿幽灵别称“鬼佬财神”，拥有吸引财富的能力，所以成为生意人的宠物，有助提高思维，开放心灵，具有招财和高度凝聚财富的力量，属正财，是代表因辛勤努力而累积的财富。 强化心脏功能，平稳情绪(紧张、失眠、愤怒、妄想)。 

💚 从绿幽灵自身的内含物的颜色来说，颜色越深当然价值就会越高，天然绿幽灵的颜色一般来说墨绿的更加稀少，喜欢的人也较多!

💚 九尾狐仙能助男女招权贵和正偏桃花，拥有万人迷的气场让人崇拜及爱慕，佩戴九尾狐仙能带来桃花财运并可使单身者拥有好姻缘、已婚者夫妻和睦、魅力十足、做事如意、招正偏财！

description:
📣 March Live Sale 📣⁠ ⁠
✨ Magnificent Mixed Minerals Part II ✨⁠
⁠
🇺🇸 A Zinc mine discovered in 1969, Elmwood Mine is one of the most prolific locality and one of the producer of the most famous Calcites. An Elmwood Calcite is not to be missed under any circumstances. Quality pieces exhibit a glassy luster and deep orange colouration. Some specimens have the sought after twinning modification, resulting in what is commonly known as Dogtooth Calcites. Elmwood pieces are extremely limited in stock due to the new mining practices from the incumbent owner prohibiting unauthorized extraction of minerals of any kind.⁠
⁠
🇲🇽 From the world famous locality of Milpillas Mine comes superb specimens of crystallised Azurite specimens. Where Azurite often forms in small minute crystals and clustered tightly, crystallisation of this size for Azurite is rarely seen. Coupled with the intense dark electric blue, the sharp crystals with exceptional form, and the depleting supply from the mine, do NOT miss this opportunity to add this collector’s piece to your cabinet!⁠
⁠
🇨🇳 A 1st generation of clear/white Scalenohedral Calcite presents as the foundation of this beautiful variety; overgrowing it is a 2nd generation of trigon Hematite-included Calcite, that gives an overall look akin to mushrooms, hence the trade name: Mushroom Calcite. On some parts of the specimen you are able to see the 1st generation of Calcite growth, giving a unique peek into the growth stages.⁠
⁠
Join us in our monthly scheduled IG live on 21 March, 8pm (GMT +8) to travel the world (remotely) with us!⁠
⁠
Limited pieces of each type available for sale~⁠⁠
.⁠⁠⁠⁠
See you soon~⁠ ⁠⁠⁠

Made with Lapis Lazuli— the crystal I associate with infinite wisdom 💙🐢, gold flakes and resin on the top layer. Pearlescent mica chroming, gold flakes, blue resin colouring and resin on the bottom layer ✨🌎 

I LIKE TURTLES! 🐢😋

“There is an Indian story — at least I heard it as an Indian story — about an Englishman who, having been told that the world rested on a platform which rested on the back of an elephant which rested in turn on the back of a turtle, asked (perhaps he was an ethnographer; it is the way they behave), what did the turtle rest on?  –Clifford Geertz, The Interpretation of Cultures

description:
📣 March Live Sale 📣⁠ ⁠
✨ Magnificent Mixed Minerals Part II ✨⁠
⁠
Join us in another episode of travelling the world with us on this special night (no VTL/passport required!) as we bring you around a few countries to explore their unique minerals right in the comfort of your own home!⁠
⁠
🇫🇷 From the high altitudes of the French Alps comes a classic specimen of white rhombohedral Calcite with black Marls inclusions. Exhibiting a gentle pink under longwave UV, these specimens are hard to come by and have been meticulously mined by hand. The rarity of the locality, and the stark contrast of white and black is definitely not to be missed!⁠
⁠
🇳🇦 Prehnite comes in many colours, from colourless to gray, yellow, green, and even white. Commonly orthorhombic in habit, our particular collection from Namibia features tiny blades of green Prehnite crystals stacked in a spherical growth, resulting in a pseudo-botryoidal look. This also gives the Prehnites a distinct etched look-alike surfacing. Keep a lookout for a mixture of shiny black Epidotes, perfect Quartz points, druzzy Quartz bed, some mysteries within the grey basalt matrix, and everything in between.⁠
⁠
🇷🇺 Septarian nodules are round concretions with a network of internal cracks, with no visible external cracks. Covering the internal surface with druzzy Pyrite of all colours, these metallic Rainbow Pyrite serves to bedazzle, and bedazzle it does! Our half-nodule iridescent Rainbow Pyrite comes from only one locality in the world, and is completely untreated.⁠
⁠
Join us in our monthly scheduled IG live on 21 March, 8pm (GMT +8) to travel the world (remotely) with us.⁠
⁠
Limited pieces of each type available for sale~⁠⁠
.⁠⁠⁠⁠
See you soon~⁠ ⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠
----------------------------⁠⁠⁠⁠

.⁠⁠⁠⁠

The translucent white nature of Selenite represents spiritual purity, light, and connection to the angelic realms. It is one of the most sacred crystals throughout history. The name ‘Selenite’ derives from the Greek goddess Selene, the goddess of the moon. 

Selenite has ability to charge and recharge all the crystals which come in its contact. With its pristine white color, it will look breathtaking next to different colored stones and crystals!

Selenite is a good stone to own that helps you to quiet your mind and give you mental clarity.

Selenite is capable of removing stagnant energies, bringing good luck, cleansing toxic energy, protection from psychic attack and clearing the home and body of negative energies etc.

Selenite is made from gypsum. You can rinse selenite in water if you must, but for five seconds only. You should never soak selenite crystals in water. It can dissolve completely. Keep selenite out of direct prolonged sunlight, as it can cause loss of luster.

Selenite scratches, chips, dents, and fractures very easily. Due to its soft nature, please expect all Selenite products to have some minor imperfections.

Something bright and cheery after the last cat-astrophe... 

Elk Creek barite on a bed of yellow calcite, from Elk Creek in Meade County, South Dakota USA 🇺🇸!

The main outstanding barite crystal is golden brown, super clear and lustrous with nice termination, although there’s some unknown frosting on the termination. The crystal sits among a whole bed of bright yellow opaque calcite crystals, most are also very well terminated, super spiky! 

Apparently less than 10% of the mined calcareous concretions in the barite zone actually contain barite when broken open. So extreme care needs to be taken during extraction as barite is very sensitive to shock and heat. 

I’m actually very sure this main barite was part of a cluster, but those got broken away, leaving only the main piece and a couple of smaller points extending from the same base.

This piece, as with most Elk Creek specimens, fluoresces a milky creamy white under uv, and phosphoresces blue/green.

The translucent white nature of Selenite represents spiritual purity, light, and connection to the angelic realms. It is one of the most sacred crystals throughout history. The name ‘Selenite’ derives from the Greek goddess Selene, the goddess of the moon. 

Selenite has ability to charge and recharge all the crystals which come in its contact. With its pristine white color, it will look breathtaking next to different colored stones and crystals!

Selenite is a good stone to own that helps you to quiet your mind and give you mental clarity.

Selenite is capable of removing stagnant energies, bringing good luck, cleansing toxic energy, protection from psychic attack and clearing the home and body of negative energies etc.

Selenite is made from gypsum. You can rinse selenite in water if you must, but for five seconds only. You should never soak selenite crystals in water. It can dissolve completely. Keep selenite out of direct prolonged sunlight, as it can cause loss of luster.

Selenite scratches, chips, dents, and fractures very easily. Due to its soft nature, please expect all Selenite products to have some minor imperfections. 

Note:
Please allow slight dimension difference due to different manual measurement. +/- 1cm.

description:
Sooooo I had this beautiful fluorite cluster from Frazer’s Hush Mine, Weardale, County Durham, England 🇬🇧

It was labeled as from Purple Pocket, which is a 2010 Rogerley’s pocket, but also labeled as from Frazer’s Hush mine, which had been closed since the 90s. I guess the mining areas are close enough such that the mislabeling to the exact mine should be fine. So although I would very much love this to be a Frazer’s Hush piece, I think Rogerley Purple pocket is the correct origin. 
Ahh provenance fun. 

This one has beautiful purple fluorescence in sunlight (1st pic), which washes out to a grey in direct sunlight, and a yellowish grey under fluorescent light (2nd pic). As with most if not all Rogerleys, this fluoresces a stunning electric blue under uv (3rd pic). 

Unfortunately, I just adopted a cat - it’s been a month and she’s generally a sweet thing. And this greedy girl jumped around some forbidden areas cos I wouldn’t give her my nasi lemak. And there. 4th pic is the aftermath of a bad jump that took half my side desk out 😭 so I was uv-ing the floor to make sure no crystal chips are left out. 

Buhbye Purple Pocket cluster. Some great cubes are no longer cubes. And I’m a bundle of emotions right now 😱🥺😔😢😭😰

💗 Rose Quartz dispels negativity & protects against environmental pollution, replacing it with loving vibes. It encourages self-forgiveness & acceptance invoking self-trust & self-worth.

💗 Rose quartz is extremely popular in Feng Shui that are used as love cures. The main reason for the stone's strength is the manganese & titanium it contains. This mineral content is particularly helpful in calming & healing the mind.

💗 粉水晶作用是招揽人脉，打开主人心怀，让主人有愉悦感，粉水晶之所以被传闻能够招来桃花，正是因为它最根本的作用是招揽人脉，很多商家会拿着粉水晶的原矿，或者雕刻件放在商铺的特殊位置，为商铺招揽人气所用。

💗 粉水晶是非常开朗的水晶之一，它会鼓励主人努力追求自己内心中的快乐，所以非常适合于自我控制能力比较强，但是并不觉得开心的人群，特别是比较内敛的人群，粉水晶能够驱散这个人群的烦躁心态，让心情平和和开心起来。很多拥有粉水晶以后，虽然没有预想的招来桃花，或者改善人脉的作用，但是却始终觉得心情愉快，正是因为这个原因。

💗 粉水晶是治愈系的水晶，它治疗心灵伤痛的效果和速度，远远在它其他的效果之上，也在其他水晶之上，所以建议一些心灵受到伤害或者遭遇一些痛苦事件的人群拥有粉水晶以安抚心灵，这个才是粉水晶最真实也是最有作用的效果。

description:
Triplite is a fairly rare mineral. The term triplite derives from the Greek word “triplos”, which means "three," alluding to the mineral's three distinct cleavage orientations. It is difficult to cut and facet due to its brittleness, high cleavage, and lack of hardness.

Triplite is able to know what each individual person is lacking and helps in that aspect. They act as a revitalizing and rejuvenating crystal in terms of balancing, increasing energy within the body and aiding in the creative mind. Aids in creating new energy for the user and being able to gain motivation that has been lost. Boosting the flow of qi throughout the body, enhancing the flow of life force within the body as well.

This crystal clears blockages in terms of life energy to ensure smooth flow and ensures that users will have the will to live and overcome any issues that come in their way. Enhancing a user with a strong mind when being in an unstable state, improves self-confidence such as being more outspoken and being easily able to reach goals. 

This crystal also improves relationships and communication with people by being able to avoid any form of arguments and criticism. Clearing any form of negative thoughts that prevent users from being able to take steps towards a goal, allows users to be able to step out of their comfort zone and eliminate bad habits to prevent themselves from being positive; inducing happiness and productivity.

Triplite is able to make the user remain calm and composed when facing issues and making decisions based on logical thinking, analysis of issues to solve the problems. Any form of manifestation will become possible with this crystal as long as effort and time are placed towards the goal, results will be shown to the user. This magnificent gemstone also helps owners to clear forms of heaviness, feeling the weight on the shoulders and weariness.

description:
✨ Alluring Amethyst Aplenty Part XVI ✨⁠⁠
⁠⁠
About 160 million years ago, when tectonic plates were rifting Africa and South America apart as the Atlantic Ocean opened, one of the world’s great flood basalt events was occurring. Basalts flowed from the rift, producing stratified lava flows thousands of feet thick in Brazil and nearby Uruguay.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Within these flows, gas bubbles and lava tubes created cavities that were first lined by a layer of agate, and then by a complete covering of coarse crystalline quartz. At this point the geodes were formed, but they were filled with rock crystal instead of amethyst. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
However, as these geodes remained buried, they were irradiated by the decay of radioactive minerals in the surrounding basalts. This radiation created color centers in the quartz, and that transformed the clear quartz into amethyst you see today in the geodes from Brazil and Uruguay.⁠⁠
⁠
The very eccentric geological phenomena have made this corner of the world an agate and amethyst paradise.⁠
⁠
Join us for Part 16 of our ‘Alluring Amethyst Aplenty’ series via IG LIVE SALE on Monday 14 March, 8pm (GMT +8)⁠⁠ to check out some beautiful Amethyst geodes and formations we have~⁠
⁠
As usual, we will feature Amethyst pieces with double crystallizations, Agate shells, Jasper shells and super colorful glitters... ⁠⁠
⁠
See you soon~ 😘⁠⁠
⁠
IG algorithms are shifting. If you like what you see, help us stay visible by Saving, Sharing, Commenting, and Liking our posts 🙏⁠

description:
Good day everyone! 

I hope you’re enjoying your Sunday afternoon😊
As you might have noticed, I’m trying a new way to reach out to you by putting photos and videos of myself alittle more often these days. 
I do not do Live Sale. Only Story Sale. 
And this is a way for me to connect with you, so you can see the person behind @thegemstoneshop - putting a face to a name. 

About Me:
My Life path is Master number 33/6 and I’m starting to grow slowly and surely into my spiritual soul path. In case you’re wondering what’s a Life Path number, you can find out yours through your date of birth. In this life journey, I have always felt an intuition and calling to reach out to others on a personal level to uplift their energy whenever I sense a person feeling down. I’m an empath and rather sensitive to the feelings and emotions of others. It is not an easy journey but I’m learning alot and growing through trials and experience as I go along. 

As some of you know, I strongly believe in the healing energies of nature. This is why I bring most of the crystal pieces to sunbathe them outdoors before launching and having them go to you. I could have easily video them indoors and sell them fast but this is not what my beliefs are with regards to healing crystals. 

My philosophy on Crystal is besides looking good on the outside, it is essential that they are genuinely energetically good for you too. The latter, in fact takes precedence over aesthetics and being perfect (just like my nose - always red on video 😆). This forms the fundamental principle and practice of @thegemstoneshop. 

With love 💝🙏🏼
Jamie

Desert rose is well known for being the perfect meditation tool that helps one stay grounded and balanced. This mineral actives our root, crown, and sacral chakras that assist in mental clarity and focus, manifestation, and self-expression, and unlocking our divine will. It's the perfect stone to place at your bedside, workspace, or meditation room as it helps cleanse one's aura and environment.

It can also help with improving communication, manifesting dreams into reality and bringing about improved intuition.

Air plants are perfect plants to display in your bedroom because they photosynthesize at night. So while you are sleeping, they emit fresh oxygen into the air. Being among plants can help reduce stress, lower blood pressure, and improve focus at home or work

Aromatherapy candles and clay can help you relax, feel calm, energized, and put your mind in a more productive mode. stimulates our limbic system, the part of the brain that is home to our memory and emotions

description:
✨ Alluring Amethyst Aplenty Part XVI ✨⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Gem-quality amethyst used to be considered just as valuable as rubies, celebrated in myth and legend. Rhea the Titan gave it to Dionysus, god of wine, to preserve his sanity from the vine. Royals and nobles sported it proudly. It even ended up in many a country's crown jewels. It remained an expensive stone, reserved only for the fortunate, right up until ginormous deposits were found in South America in the 1800s. ⁠
⁠
One begins to dig until one encounters traces of Geodes or Druze. Sometimes Days and weeks pass without result and sometimes you find one day wonders… If you find geodes in larger dimensions, you have to carefully knock around the Geode, the Geode must not be destroyed. It takes a lot of patience, skill and professionalism to take out the Geode as a whole – without it breaking apart. ⁠
⁠
Join us for Part 16 of our ‘Alluring Amethyst Aplenty’ series via IG LIVE SALE on Monday 14 March, 8pm (GMT +8)⁠⁠ to check out some beautiful Amethyst geodes and formations we have~⁠
⁠
As usual, we will feature Amethyst pieces with double crystallizations, Agate shells, Jasper shells and super colorful glitters... ⁠⁠
⁠
See you soon~ 😘⁠⁠
⁠
IG algorithms are shifting. If you like what you see, help us stay visible by Saving, Sharing, Commenting, and Liking our posts 🙏⁠

description:
Dumortierite in and around quartz. Or maybe, quartz in and on dumortierite?🤍💎💙 

Some of the quartz have superb clarity, but they are all so white and clean looking! Great contrast with the beautiful deep blue dumortierite. 
The underside has some great little caves where more of the needles are exposed, very frosty feels 🥶

So hard to get a good sharp focus and lighting on the teeny thin blues though... 
I’ve seen plenty of dumortierite in and dusted on quartz faces, but hardly much balls of exposed needles. 

This beauty from Vaca Morte quarry, Bahia, Brazil 🇧🇷 which produces amazing pieces with simply fantastical landscapes of blue in quartz!

description:
<AJOITE INCLUDED QUARTZ>

Messina Mine, Musina, Limpopo, South Africa

Ajoite is one of the rarest inclusions in quartz. It's a secondary mineral from the oxidisation of other secondary copper minerals and can be found only in Arizona, Zimbabwe and South Africa.

This piece with druzy quartz base comes with turquoise saturation in several baby points. One of the tiny points has black hematite amidst the ajoite inclusion (see second last slide).

DM us if you would like to add a piece of ajoite to your collection! 💕 

Price is in $1xx range.

Due to the rarity, prices of ajoite can get pretty crazy. Fake (or misidentified) ajoite is usually a off greenish shade while genuine ajoite has a more bluish green shade 💙

Measures 7.2cm length, 5cm height. Comes in specimen box.

description:
✨ Alluring Amethyst Aplenty Part XVI ✨⁠⁠
⁠⁠
A stalactite from the Greek 'stalaktos' ('dripping') via stalassein ('to drip') is a mineral formation that hangs from the ceiling of caves, hot springs, or man-made structures such as bridges and mines. The combination of both amethyst and stalactites is very rare and found in only a few places in the world. ⁠
⁠
The amethyst stalactites are named after similar occurrences of limestone deposits in cave formations.  Stalactites form as water laden with calcium carbonate drips from the roof of caves. As the dripping continues, layers of calcite are deposited in rings and over time they settle on top of each other creating the stalactite. ⁠
⁠
When stalactites develop, they are under the influence of gravity and tend to develop straight down. But sometimes an outside influence like air currents or even the direction of flow of the invading solution can cause a curvature or thickening on one side of the stalactite that can influence the overall shape or direction. ⁠
⁠
Join us for Part 16 of our ‘Alluring Amethyst Aplenty’ series via IG LIVE SALE on Monday 14 March, 8pm (GMT +8)⁠⁠ to check out some beautiful Amethyst geodes and formations we have~⁠
⁠
As usual, we will feature Amethyst pieces with double crystallizations, Agate shells, Jasper shells and super colorful glitters... ⁠⁠
⁠
See you soon~ 😘⁠⁠
⁠
IG algorithms are shifting. If you like what you see, help us stay visible by Saving, Sharing, Commenting, and Liking our posts 🙏⁠

description:
Chinese Lacquer Bangle 大漆

According to historical records, China is the first country in the world to use lacquer. The Chinese lacquer with brilliant colour is waterproof, corrosion-proof and high temperature resistant. It is one of China’s great inventions of industrial arts.

Lacquer ware refers to using lacquer to paint on the surface of wares or artwork. After being heated and mixed with pigments, colorful lacquer comes into being and can be made as delicate handicrafts. 

Besides the ornamental furniture and various kinds of wares, lacquer ware can used as musical instruments and weapons.

description:
✨ Alluring Amethyst Aplenty Part XVI ✨⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Residing within the deep mines of Catalán Grande, in the birthplace of the most beautiful Amethyst Geodes, Crystamour is proud to present to all our supporters a small collection of unique Uruguay Amethyst formations some with Calcite growths! ⁠
⁠
Calcite is considered a cleansing stone that encourages spiritual awareness while Amethyst calms the mind. Together, both create a soothing combination of energies fit for a meditation room.⁠
⁠
Amethyst is a purple variety of quartz. It is part of the hexagonal crystal system. Said to be the bridge that connects the concrete with the divine - the meaning of Amethyst has long been synonymous with spirituality and is famed for its close association with both the third eye and the crown chakra.⁠
⁠
Join us for Part 16 of our ‘Alluring Amethyst Aplenty’ series via IG LIVE SALE on Monday 14 March, 8pm (GMT +8)⁠⁠ to check out some beautiful Amethyst geodes and formations we have~⁠
⁠
As usual, we will feature Amethyst pieces with double crystallizations, Agate shells, Jasper shells and super colorful glitters... ⁠⁠
⁠
See you soon~ 😘⁠⁠

IG algorithms are shifting. If you like what you see, help us stay visible by Saving, Sharing, Commenting, and Liking our posts 🙏⁠
